# Terraform (iac/) — deploy PRD §Terraform. State lives in the kubernetes backend, not locally;
# tfvars hold secrets (image tags, DB password, Cloudflare token, kubeconfig path).
# `.terraform.lock.hcl` is intentionally NOT ignored — commit it for reproducible provider installs.
iac/.terraform/
iac/terraform.tfvars
iac/*.auto.tfvars
iac/terraform.tfvars.json
iac/*.tfstate
iac/*.tfstate.*
iac/*.tfplan
